    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-08-24T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-08-24T00:00:00-05:00" n="108" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d108">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Denby</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-08-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 24, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.
                                (Received Oct. 8.)</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 2322.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inform you that I sent
                            the following telegram to Foochow on the 21st instant: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p rend="flushleft">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Hixson</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Foochow:</hi>
                        </p>
                        <p>Have demanded that authorities cooperate with you; that an
                                    official be delegated for the purpose; that you be present at
                                    examination, and no obstruction offered.</p>
                        <p rend="right">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Denby</hi>.</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Charles Denby</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
